data.description:
Fully Renovated Townhouse Style Apartment with 2 bedrooms, Washer, Dryer, Gas Stove, Fridge included.

Property not approved for section 8.

Tenant pays Gas, Water, Electricity. (Gas heating baseboard)

Landlord pays Sewer, Trash, Recycling, Stormwater.

First Month's Rent & Security due on Signing.

A background check on all resident over 18. ($45 non-refundable fee per person).

Applicant(s) must be non-smoker.

Applicant must exhibit a responsible financial life. Credit score minimum of 650.

Applicant must have current photo identification & a valid social security number.

Applicant's monthly household income must exceed three times the rent. Income must be from a verifiable source. Unverifiable income will not be considered.

Applicants must receive positive references from all landlords for the previous 5 years.

Applicant may not have any evictions or unpaid judgments from previous landlords.

No pets allowed in the property.

Max occupancy: 3
